"title": "1035: God, faithfulness of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1035: god, faithfulness of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's perfect loyalty and consistency in being true to his name, his character and his word.</p>\n<h2>God's faithfulness is an integral part of his nature</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num23:19\">NUM 23:19</a></strong> <em>God's limitless power and steadfast love imply complete faithfulness which contrasts with human nature</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:22-Lam3:23\">LAM 3:22–3:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:6\">EXO 34:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:8-Deut7:9\">DEU 7:8–7:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:4\">DEU 32:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:21\">ROM 4:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:13\">2TI 2:13</a></p>\n<h2>God is faithful to his name and character</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:13\">2TI 2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:8\">NEH 9:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:8\">PSA 106:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:24\">1TH 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:13-Heb6:18\">HEB 6:13–6:18</a></p>\n<h2>God's faithfulness is known through fulfilled promises</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:14\">JOS 23:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh21:45\">JOS 21:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:56\">1KI 8:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:15\">1CH 16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:13\">PSA 145:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:9\">2PE 3:9</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of God's faithfulness in fulfilled promises</h2>\n<h3>Abraham's fatherhood</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:2-Gen12:3\">GEN 12:2–12:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:4\">GEN 15:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:1-Gen21:2\">GEN 21:1–21:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:9\">ROM 9:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:28\">GAL 4:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:13-Heb6:15\">HEB 6:13–6:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:11\">HEB 11:11</a></p>\n<h3>The building of the temple</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:12-2Sam7:13\">2SA 7:12–7:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:11-1Chr17:12\">1CH 17:11–17:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:17-1Kgs8:21\">1KI 8:17–8:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:7-2Chr6:11\">2CH 6:7–6:11</a></p>\n<h3>The exile in Babylon</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:8-Jer25:11\">JER 25:8–25:11</a></strong> <em>God's faithfulness will not always mean human prosperity.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:8-2Kgs25:12\">2KI 25:8–25:12</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:17-2Chr36:21\">2CH 36:17–36:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:12-Jer52:16\">JER 52:12–52:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra1:1-Ezra1:3\">EZR 1:1–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:27\">JER 52:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:10\">JER 29:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:2-Dan9:3\">DAN 9:2–9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:15-Dan9:19\">DAN 9:15–9:19</a></p>\n<h2>God's faithfulness is revealed to the faithful</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:26\">2SA 22:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:14\">GAL 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:23\">HEB 10:23</a></p>\n<h2>God's faithfulness is constant</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:3-Rom3:4\">ROM 3:3–3:4</a></strong> <em>God's faithfulness is not negated by human unfaithfulness.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:25\">EZK 12:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:3\">HAB 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:13\">2TI 2:13</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is the ultimate evidence of God's faithfulness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:32-Acts13:33\">ACT 13:32–13:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:9-John14:11\">JHN 14:9–14:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:8-Rom15:9\">ROM 15:8–15:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:20-2Cor1:22\">2CO 1:20–1:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:2-Heb3:6\">HEB 3:2–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:5\">REV 1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:11\">REV 19:11</a></p>",
